data.description: Come home today in the coveted Buffalo Crossing subdivision of Cibolo. This home has gorgeous wood flooring in the living spaces with a wonderful open floorplan layout. The family and dining areas are very spacious and will make for a great space to spend time with family and friends. The upgraded kitchen is beautiful and features an island with a smooth cooktop, smooth countertops, a tiled backsplash. The master suite is separate from the secondary rooms for additional privacy and features a full en-suite bathroom that includes a separate walk-in shower as well as an garden tub with several water features.  A stunning large covered patio with stairs to the garden area is the highlight of this home. This additional space is great for hanging out, playing, and entertaining. You will love this well-maintained home.  Call today to schedule your showing.
